---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Disclaimer"
  description="What HealthMaps is and isn't: general information about Australia's mental health system, not medical advice."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section>
    <div class="max-w-body mx-auto px-4 pt-16 md:pt-24 pb-12 md:pb-16">
      <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-body font-semibold mb-3">Site policy</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-heading mb-5 tracking-[-0.01em] leading-tight">Disclaimer</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-body leading-relaxed max-w-[36rem]">
        Plain-language version first: this site explains how the system works. It doesn't know your
        situation, and it's not a substitute for a health professional who does.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-paper-cream">
    <div class="max-w-body mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-20 space-y-14 md:space-y-16">
      <!-- REVIEW: all sections below are AI-drafted — please review wording, and consider a legal once-over before launch -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mb-4">General information, not medical advice</h2>
        <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
          Everything on HealthMaps is general information about navigating the Australian mental health
          system. It is not medical, psychological or legal advice, and it isn't tailored to your
          circumstances. Nothing here can diagnose a condition or tell you which treatment is right for
          you. For advice about your own health, see a GP or a qualified mental health professional.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl bg-white border border-border shadow-sm p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">This is not a crisis service</h2>
        <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
          HealthMaps is an information website — no one monitors it, and we can't respond to urgent
          situations.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-5 border-t border-border divide-y divide-border">
          <div class="py-4 flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-4 gap-y-1">
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">If you or someone else is in immediate danger</p>
            <a href="tel:000" class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-primary whitespace-nowrap">000</a>
          </div>
          <div class="py-4 flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-x-4 gap-y-1">
            <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">If you're in crisis or need to talk to someone now — Lifeline, free and available 24/7</p>
            <a href="tel:131114" class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-primary whitespace-nowrap">13 11 14</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-body mt-4">
          More crisis options are in the "Urgent help" button on every page.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="divide-y divide-border border-t border-border">
        <div class="py-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">Costs and Medicare figures are estimates</h2>
          <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
            Fees, gap payments and Medicare rebates change over time and vary between practitioners and
            locations. Figures on this site — including the cost calculator — are indicative estimates to
            help you plan, not quotes. Always confirm fees and rebates with the practice before you book,
            and check current rebate amounts with
            <a href="https://www.servicesaustralia.gov.au/medicare" class="text-primary font-semibold underline underline-offset-2" rel="noopener">Services Australia</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="py-8">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-heading mb-3">Keeping information current</h2>
          <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
            We do our best to keep information accurate and up to date, and we correct errors when we find
            them or when readers point them out. Even so, details — especially costs, rebate amounts and
            referral rules — can change before we catch up. If something here looks out of date, please
            tell us at
            <a href="mailto:jethrohedstrom@gmail.com" class="text-primary font-semibold underline underline-offset-2">jethrohedstrom@gmail.com</a>.
            <!-- REVIEW: if you commit to a review cadence on the About page, mirror it here -->
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-10 border-t border-border">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-heading mb-4">No endorsements</h2>
        <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
          HealthMaps is independent. We don't accept payment from practitioners or services, and a
          mention of any service type on this site is explanation, not endorsement. Links to external
          websites are provided for convenience; we aren't responsible for their content.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
